The Suit is a 5 part villian group.  It is the Jokers, Clubs, Diamonds, Hearts, and Spades.

The two Jokers, are the fraternal twins that run the overall group.  
Brother and Sister, the children of a Mob Boss of the 'old guard' that was killed while they were kids.
They swore to bring down organized crime, in one way or another.  They decided that they would do it from the inside to start, then move out to their own crew.

The Clubs
    The clubs are in charge of the 'gambling' aspect of an organized crime syndicate.  Their main base is in Los Vegas.
